c: 5
v: 31
t: "Nuko Allah yohereza icyiyoni gicukura mu butaka (gihamba kigenzi cyacyo), kugira ngo kimwereke uko ashyingura umuvandimwe we. (Gahini) aravuga ati “Mbega ibyago! Ubu koko nananiwe kuba nk’iki cyiyoni ngo nshyingure umuvandimwe wanjye?” Ubwo aba abaye mu bicuza (icyatumye yica umuvandimwe we)"